OL,3,C#46m bridge finally set to open ending
OL,4,C12 mile diversion for drivers
OL,6,FA new road connecting north and south
OL,7,FWales is set to open on Friday 2
OL,8,FFebruary, meaning drivers will no
OL,9,Flonger face a 12 mile diversion.
OL,11,FThe Dyfi Bridge near has been built to
OL,12,Freplace the Pont-ar-Ddyfi bridge,
OL,13,Fwhich was unable to carry the current
OL,14,Fvolume of traffic and was often closed
OL,15,Fdue to flooding.
OL,17,FThe new structure has been funded by
OL,18,Fthe to the tune of #46 million with it
OL,19,Ffacing delays in its completion. It
OL,20,Fwas originally due to be finished in
OL,21,Fspring 2023.
