OL,6,F"I was particularly pleased to be
OL,7,Famong the first group of people on
OL,8,Fbikes to take advantage of the new
OL,9,Fcycling and walking route that is
OL,10,Ffully integrated into the new bridge,
OL,11,Fas part of a wider active travel
OL,12,Fnetwork being developed in and around
OL,13,FMachynlleth.
OL,15,F"This shows how we can make it easier
OL,16,Fto walk and cycle in rural Wales, as
OL,17,Fwell as in our more urban towns and
OL,18,Fcities."
