OL,6,FThe Deputy Minister continued: "Our
OL,7,Froads policy statement published last
OL,8,Fyear makes clear that we will continue
OL,9,Fto invest in new and existing roads,
OL,10,Fbut to qualify for future funding the
OL,11,Ffocus must be on minimising carbon
OL,12,Femissions, not increasing capacity;
OL,13,Fnot increasing emissions through
OL,14,Fhigher vehicle speeds, and not
OL,15,Fadversely affecting ecologically
OL,16,Fvaluable sites.
