OL,9,Fput into law a requirement to reach
OL,10,FNetZero by 2050.
OL,12,F"We must be prepared to follow
OL,13,Fthrough."
OL,15,FDavid Parr, Managing Director of
OL,16,FGriffiths Civil Engineering, who built
OL,17,Fthe bridge, added: "We are proud to
OL,18,Fsee the Dyfi Bridge Scheme open to the
OL,19,Fpublic.
