OL,6,F"The scheme has been a real technical
OL,7,Fchallenge but is testament to our
OL,8,Fcommitment to addressing the effects
OL,9,Fof climate change, enhancing community
OL,10,Faccess to essential healthcare and
OL,11,Feducation services, all whilst
OL,12,Ffocussing on active travel solutions.
OL,14,F"Through collective efforts, we have
OL,15,Fnot only reduced our carbon footprint
OL,16,Ffrom construction but also invested in
OL,17,Ffuture generations through nurturing
OL,18,Ftalents through apprenticeships."
